Subject: drm/i915: Add intel_digital_port lock/unlock hooks
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: 9210e94a5a3bf7fc84b3d94dd5d2099ca434931b
